                  <summary><p>A composite manuscript containing leaves of various format and state of preservation. Contains medical treatises, that is <foreign xml:lang="ta">cūttiram</foreign>s by Pōkar, Akattiyar, Rōmarici, and Piramamuṉi (see U1, <locus facs="7">table of contents</locus>).</p>
<p>The bundle is too fragile to be manipulated and exhaustively examined.</p>  
<p>Description based on the summary examination of the original manuscript (September 2021).</p>
<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p>      


